name: TemPsy-Suite
body:
Welcome to TemPsy-Suite
==========

TemPsy-Suite is a toolset to perform offline checking and violation inspection of *TemPsy* properties on system execution traces. The toolset has been developed by [Wei Dou](http://people.svv.lu/dou), at the [SVV lab](http://www.svv.lu) of the [University of Luxembourg](http://wwwen.uni.lu).
